  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514430/extras/5261c5683746899083b2d1ae23b9d651.avif?t=1762539820\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br><br>A sandbox strategy game where you control Reek and Havok; two devilish creatures that aim to destabilize a town through chaos and destruction.<br><br>Disguised as a civilian, they can poison wells, pollute the food, start fires and disrupt supply caravans, all whilst evading the law.<br>The town itself will try and fix the damage caused, as well as bring the fiends to justice. This is where discretion and careful planning are key!<br><br>Feel free to contact us through the community hub, your feedback and suggestions are invaluable to improving the quality of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514430/extras/977403b19674ea57158236376e424de4.avif?t=1762539820\" width=600 height=96 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514430/extras/5261c5683746899083b2d1ae23b9d651.avif?t=1762539820\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br><br>A sandbox strategy game where you control Reek and Havok; two devilish creatures that aim to destabilize a town through chaos and destruction.<br><br>Disguised as a civilian, they can poison wells, pollute the food, start fires and disrupt supply caravans, all whilst evading the law.<br>The town itself will try and fix the damage caused, as well as bring the fiends to justice. This is where discretion and careful planning are key!<br><br>Feel free to contact us through the community hub, your feedback and suggestions are invaluable to improving the quality of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514430/extras/977403b19674ea57158236376e424de4.avif?t=1762539820\" width=600 height=96 /></span>",
